{"tid":1590510,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣新手 每人做多一點點 10.1國殤大遊行","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:39:39.000Z","uid":237207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79219d1ba83d48139b73a948c1b51087f0e7fdfd","tid":1590510,"uid":237207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSh5Oaj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSh5Oaj.jpg&h=fd9eab6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺九月靜左好多 唔知係大家攰定係手足俾人拉晒<br />\n但係只要每個人都願意付出多少少 成件事就會好唔同<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9.28 添馬公園集會</span></span><br />\n時間：1900-2100<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要塞爆添馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">10.1 民陣國殤大遊行</span></span><br />\n1400東角道集合<br />\n1500出發遊行至遮打道<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔單止要話俾自己聽，仲要話俾全世界聽，中共係點樣踐踏人權民主自由，點樣毒害全世界</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">每當我地覺得自己攰，覺得自己驚，就諗下犧牲左自己生命既手足，被自殺既手足，同埋仲奮戰緊既手足。而家選擇放棄，或者抱住其他人去我唔洗去既心態，咁呢場革命就好快玩完。好坦白講，與其擔心和理非割蓆，不如都多謝勇武bb唔拋棄我地。我地和理非細膽，又或者有其他包袱，勇武bb做左好多我地想做而唔敢做既事。和理非既然未ready做勇武，唔緊要，我地就要做好我地和理非既責任，就係勇敢企出黎，塞爆港島。香港人齊上齊落，加油</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不是看見希望而堅持<br />\n而是堅持所以看見希望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共黨，光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"8df94871f963a50e6a05a3f20aa384d3dcf1919d","tid":1590510,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"0872419fc88a096402aad80ca59332309232a06e","tid":1590510,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10.1 民陣國殤大遊行<br />\n1400東角道集合<br />\n1500出發遊行至遮打道</span></span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"830a1c2c77bd6855f793605c702a1c67c7c4bba3","tid":1590510,"uid":325446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:25:37.000Z","msg":"[人面識別] 你以為剩係電燈柱先有？黨企中國海外/中國建築地盤會裝人面識別系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576481\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94bf88ab5a69682dc5bf18ac086923ad34a45fcc","tid":1590510,"uid":210912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a42b28999346db539975f300c1647fe0a9f1ec27","tid":1590510,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做得忍者，一定要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzvXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzvXH8.jpg&h=b6574070&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}